---
import DocsLayout from '../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<DocsLayout title="Configuration" activeNav="configuration" description="Complete configuration reference for all Araxys security modules with environment variable support.">

  <h2 id="overview">Overview</h2>
  <p>
    Araxys uses <strong>Pydantic Settings</strong> for configuration, which means every setting supports <strong>environment variables</strong> with the <code>ARAXYS_</code> prefix. You can configure Araxys programmatically, via environment variables, or a combination of both.
  </p>

  <h2 id="environment-variables">Environment Variables</h2>

  <div class="code-block">
    <div class="code-block-header">
      <span class="code-block-lang">bash</span>
      <button class="code-block-copy">Copy</button>
    </div>
    <pre><code><span class="token-comment"># Required</span>
<span class="token-keyword">export</span> <span class="token-param">ARAXYS_SECRET_KEY</span>=<span class="token-string">"your-production-secret-key-here!"</span>

<span class="token-comment"># Optional — enables Redis backends</span>
<span class="token-keyword">export</span> <span class="token-param">ARAXYS_REDIS_URL</span>=<span class="token-string">"redis://localhost:6379"</span></code></pre>
  </div>

  <h2 id="master-config">AraxysConfig (Master)</h2>
  <p>The root configuration object that contains all module configs:</p>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Field</th>
        <th>Type</th>
        <th>Default</th>
        <th>Env Variable</th>
        <th>Description</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>secret_key</code></td><td><code>str</code></td><td><em>required</em></td><td><code>ARAXYS_SECRET_KEY</code></td><td>Master secret (min 32 chars) — used for JWT signing + audit encryption</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>redis_url</code></td><td><code>str | None</code></td><td><code>None</code></td><td><code>ARAXYS_REDIS_URL</code></td><td>Redis URL. If set, enables Redis backends for rate limiting + JWT.</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>rate_limit</code></td><td><code>RateLimitConfig</code></td><td>defaults</td><td>—</td><td>Rate limiting settings</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>honeypot</code></td><td><code>HoneypotConfig</code></td><td>defaults</td><td>—</td><td>Honeypot trap settings</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>jwt</code></td><td><code>JWTConfig</code></td><td>defaults</td><td>—</td><td>JWT token settings</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>secure_headers</code></td><td><code>SecureHeadersConfig</code></td><td>defaults</td><td>—</td><td>Security headers settings</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>sanitize</code></td><td><code>SanitizeConfig</code></td><td>defaults</td><td>—</td><td>Payload sanitization settings</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>audit</code></td><td><code>AuditConfig</code></td><td>defaults</td><td>—</td><td>Audit logging settings</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>cors</code></td><td><code>CORSConfig | None</code></td><td><code>None</code></td><td>—</td><td>CORS policy configuration</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>ip_access</code></td><td><code>IPAccessConfig | None</code></td><td><code>None</code></td><td>—</td><td>IP access control configuration</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>csrf</code></td><td><code>CSRFConfig | None</code></td><td><code>None</code></td><td>—</td><td>CSRF protection configuration</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>brute_force</code></td><td><code>BruteForceConfig | None</code></td><td><code>None</code></td><td>—</td><td>Brute force + password policy</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>session</code></td><td><code>SessionConfig | None</code></td><td><code>None</code></td><td>—</td><td>Session management (max_concurrent, session_ttl, idle_timeout_seconds)</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>otel</code></td><td><code>OTelConfig | None</code></td><td><code>None</code></td><td>—</td><td>OpenTelemetry configuration</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>webhooks</code></td><td><code>WebhookConfig | None</code></td><td><code>None</code></td><td>—</td><td>Security webhooks configuration</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>webauthn</code></td><td><code>WebAuthnConfig | None</code></td><td><code>None</code></td><td>—</td><td>WebAuthn / Passkeys configuration (v0.10)</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>redis</code></td><td><code>dict | None</code></td><td><code>None</code></td><td>—</td><td>Redis HA mode: sentinel/cluster config (v0.10)</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>prometheus</code></td><td><code>PrometheusConfig | None</code></td><td><code>None</code></td><td>—</td><td>Prometheus metrics configuration</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>prompt_injection</code></td><td><code>PromptInjectionConfig | None</code></td><td><code>None</code></td><td>—</td><td>Prompt Injection Detection settings (v0.11)</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>scan_files</code></td><td><code>FileScanConfig | None</code></td><td><code>None</code></td><td>—</td><td>File scan settings for prompt injection (v0.11)</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>malware</code></td><td><code>MalwareConfig | None</code></td><td><code>None</code></td><td>—</td><td>Malware Scanning settings (v0.12)</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2 id="full-example">Full Configuration Example</h2>

  <div class="code-block">
    <div class="code-block-header">
      <span class="code-block-lang">python</span>
      <button class="code-block-copy">Copy</button>
    </div>
    <pre><code><span class="token-keyword">from</span> araxys <span class="token-keyword">import</span> AraxysConfig, AraxysShield
<span class="token-keyword">from</span> araxys.core.config <span class="token-keyword">import</span> (
    RateLimitConfig,
    HoneypotConfig,
    JWTConfig,
    SecureHeadersConfig,
    SanitizeConfig,
    AuditConfig,
    PromptInjectionConfig,
    MalwareConfig,
)

config = <span class="token-function">AraxysConfig</span>(
    <span class="token-param">secret_key</span>=<span class="token-string">"generate-with-openssl-rand-hex-32!"</span>,
    <span class="token-param">redis_url</span>=<span class="token-string">"redis://localhost:6379"</span>,

        <span class="token-param">rate_limit</span>=<span class="token-function">RateLimitConfig</span>(
        <span class="token-param">max_requests</span>=<span class="token-number">200</span>,
        <span class="token-param">window_seconds</span>=<span class="token-number">120</span>,
        <span class="token-param">ban_threshold</span>=<span class="token-number">10</span>,
        <span class="token-param">ban_duration_seconds</span>=<span class="token-number">600</span>,
        <span class="token-param">max_ban_duration_seconds</span>=<span class="token-number">7200</span>,
        <span class="token-param">escalation_multiplier</span>=<span class="token-number">3.0</span>,
    ),

    <span class="token-param">honeypot</span>=<span class="token-function">HoneypotConfig</span>(
        <span class="token-param">paths</span>=[<span class="token-string">"/admin"</span>, <span class="token-string">"/wp-login.php"</span>, <span class="token-string">"/.git/config"</span>],
        <span class="token-param">ban_duration_seconds</span>=<span class="token-number">7200</span>,
    ),

    <span class="token-param">jwt</span>=<span class="token-function">JWTConfig</span>(
        <span class="token-param">access_token_ttl_minutes</span>=<span class="token-number">15</span>,
        <span class="token-param">refresh_token_ttl_days</span>=<span class="token-number">30</span>,
    ),

    <span class="token-param">secure_headers</span>=<span class="token-function">SecureHeadersConfig</span>(
        <span class="token-param">hsts_max_age</span>=<span class="token-number">31_536_000</span>,
        <span class="token-param">content_security_policy</span>=<span class="token-string">"default-src 'self'"</span>,
    ),

    <span class="token-param">sanitize</span>=<span class="token-function">SanitizeConfig</span>(
        <span class="token-param">max_depth</span>=<span class="token-number">15</span>,
        <span class="token-param">exclude_paths</span>=[<span class="token-string">"/upload"</span>],
    ),

    <span class="token-param">audit</span>=<span class="token-function">AuditConfig</span>(
        <span class="token-param">encrypt</span>=<span class="token-bool">True</span>,
        <span class="token-param">log_file</span>=<span class="token-string">"/var/log/araxys/audit.log"</span>,
    ),

    <span class="token-param">prompt_injection</span>=<span class="token-function">PromptInjectionConfig</span>(
        <span class="token-param">enabled</span>=<span class="token-bool">True</span>,
        <span class="token-param">detectors</span>=[<span class="token-string">"all"</span>],
        <span class="token-param">threshold</span>=<span class="token-number">0.8</span>,
    ),

    <span class="token-param">malware</span>=<span class="token-function">MalwareConfig</span>(
        <span class="token-param">enabled</span>=<span class="token-bool">True</span>,
        <span class="token-param">detectors</span>=[<span class="token-string">"all"</span>],
        <span class="token-param">archive_bomb_max_ratio</span>=<span class="token-number">10.0</span>,
    ),
)</code></pre>
  </div>

  <h2 id="redis-ha">Redis High Availability (v0.10)</h2>
  <p>
    Araxys v0.10 introduces <strong>Redis Sentinel and Cluster</strong> support. All Araxys backends (rate limiting, sessions, JWT, DLQ) auto-detect the pool based on the <code>mode</code> field:
  </p>

  <div class="code-block">
    <div class="code-block-header">
      <span class="code-block-lang">python</span>
      <button class="code-block-copy">Copy</button>
    </div>
    <pre><code set:html={`<span class="token-comment"># Sentinel mode — automatic failover</span>
config = <span class="token-function">AraxysConfig</span>(
    <span class="token-param">secret_key</span>=<span class="token-string">"..."</span>,
    <span class="token-param">redis</span>={
        <span class="token-string">"mode"</span>: <span class="token-string">"sentinel"</span>,
        <span class="token-string">"sentinels"</span>: [(<span class="token-string">"sentinel1"</span>, <span class="token-number">26379</span>), (<span class="token-string">"sentinel2"</span>, <span class="token-number">26379</span>)],
        <span class="token-string">"master_name"</span>: <span class="token-string">"araxys-master"</span>,
    },
)

<span class="token-comment"># Cluster mode — client-side sharding</span>
config = <span class="token-function">AraxysConfig</span>(
    <span class="token-param">secret_key</span>=<span class="token-string">"..."</span>,
    <span class="token-param">redis</span>={
        <span class="token-string">"mode"</span>: <span class="token-string">"cluster"</span>,
        <span class="token-string">"startup_nodes"</span>: [(<span class="token-string">"node1"</span>, <span class="token-number">6379</span>), (<span class="token-string">"node2"</span>, <span class="token-number">6379</span>)],
    },
)`} /></pre>
  </div>

  <h2 id="secure-headers-config">Secure Headers Configuration</h2>
  <p>The secure headers middleware injects OWASP-recommended security headers into every response:</p>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Header</th>
        <th>Default Value</th>
        <th>Config Field</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>Strict-Transport-Security</code></td><td><code>max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains</code></td><td><code>hsts_max_age</code>, <code>hsts_include_subdomains</code></td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>X-Content-Type-Options</code></td><td><code>nosniff</code></td><td><code>content_type_nosniff</code></td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>X-Frame-Options</code></td><td><code>DENY</code></td><td><code>frame_options</code></td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>X-XSS-Protection</code></td><td><code>0</code> (disabled — modern best practice)</td><td>—</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>Referrer-Policy</code></td><td><code>strict-origin-when-cross-origin</code></td><td><code>referrer_policy</code></td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>Content-Security-Policy</code></td><td>Not set (configurable)</td><td><code>content_security_policy</code></td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>Permissions-Policy</code></td><td>Not set (configurable)</td><td><code>permissions_policy</code></td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2 id="production-recommendations">Production Recommendations</h2>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Aspect</th>
        <th>Recommendation</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><strong>Backends</strong></td><td>Use Redis (<code>araxys[redis]</code>) for multi-worker deployments</td></tr>
      <tr><td><strong>Secret Key</strong></td><td>Generate with <code>openssl rand -hex 32</code> — never hardcode</td></tr>
      <tr><td><strong>API Key Storage</strong></td><td>Implement <code>APIKeyStorage</code> protocol with your database</td></tr>
      <tr><td><strong>Audit Logs</strong></td><td>Enable encryption + write to a dedicated log file</td></tr>
      <tr><td><strong>Rate Limits</strong></td><td>Tune <code>max_requests</code> per endpoint for your traffic patterns</td></tr>
      <tr><td><strong>HTTPS</strong></td><td>Always deploy behind TLS — HSTS headers expect it</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2 id="module-configs">Module Configurations</h2>
  <p>Araxys provides the following configuration classes for its security module suite:</p>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Config Class</th>
        <th>Module</th>
        <th>Key Fields</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>CORSConfig</code></td><td>CORS Policy</td><td><code>allowed_origins</code>, <code>allowed_methods</code></td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>IPAccessConfig</code></td><td>IP Access Control</td><td><code>mode</code>, <code>allowed_ips</code>, <code>blocked_ips</code></td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>CSRFConfig</code></td><td>CSRF Protection</td><td><code>cookie_name</code>, <code>token_ttl</code></td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>BruteForceConfig</code></td><td>Brute Force</td><td><code>max_attempts</code>, <code>password_rules</code></td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>SessionConfig</code></td><td>Sessions</td><td><code>max_concurrent</code>, <code>session_ttl</code></td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>OTelConfig</code></td><td>OpenTelemetry</td><td><code>service_name</code>, <code>exporter_endpoint</code></td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>WebhookConfig</code></td><td>Webhooks</td><td><code>webhook_url</code>, <code>events</code></td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>PrometheusConfig</code></td><td>Metrics</td><td><code>metrics_path</code></td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>WebAuthnConfig</code></td><td>WebAuthn (v0.10)</td><td><code>rp_name</code>, <code>rp_id</code>, <code>origin</code></td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>WebhookDLQConfig</code></td><td>Webhook DLQ (v0.10)</td><td><code>dlq_enabled</code>, <code>dlq_ttl_seconds</code></td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>PromptInjectionConfig</code></td><td>Prompt Injection (v0.11)</td><td><code>enabled</code>, <code>detectors</code>, <code>threshold</code>, <code>file_scan</code></td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>FileScanConfig</code></td><td>Prompt Injection File Scan (v0.11)</td><td><code>enabled</code>, <code>scan_images</code>, <code>scan_pdf</code>, <code>scan_office</code></td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>MalwareConfig</code></td><td>Malware Scanning (v0.12)</td><td><code>enabled</code>, <code>detectors</code>, <code>archive_bomb_max_ratio</code></td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <p>
    All config classes default to <code>None</code> in the master <code>AraxysConfig</code>, meaning modules are disabled until explicitly configured. Install all optional dependencies with:
  </p>

  <div class="code-block">
    <div class="code-block-header">
      <span class="code-block-lang">bash</span>
      <button class="code-block-copy">Copy</button>
    </div>
    <pre><code><span class="token-comment"># Install Araxys with ALL optional dependencies</span>
pip install araxys[all]

<span class="token-comment"># Prompt Injection — text only</span>
pip install araxys[prompt_injection]

<span class="token-comment"># Prompt Injection — with file scanning</span>
pip install araxys[prompt_injection_scan]

<span class="token-comment"># Specific file scanning extras</span>
pip install araxys[prompt-guard-image]
pip install araxys[prompt-guard-pdf]
pip install araxys[prompt-guard-office]</code></pre>
  </div>

  <h2 id="prompt-injection-config">PromptInjectionConfig (v0.11)</h2>
  <p>Configures the <a href="/prompt-injection">Prompt Injection Guard</a> module. All fields are optional.</p>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Field</th>
        <th>Type</th>
        <th>Default</th>
        <th>Description</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>enabled</code></td><td><code>bool</code></td><td><code>True</code></td><td>Enable/disable prompt injection detection</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>detectors</code></td><td><code>list[str]</code></td><td><code>["all"]</code></td><td>Subset of detectors: <code>"direct_injection"</code>, <code>"jailbreak"</code>, <code>"delimiter_escape"</code>, <code>"zero_width"</code>, <code>"homoglyphs"</code></td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>file_scan</code></td><td><code>FileScanConfig | None</code></td><td><code>None</code></td><td>File scanning configuration</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>exclude_paths</code></td><td><code>list[str]</code></td><td><code>[]</code></td><td>Paths excluded from scanning</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>threshold</code></td><td><code>float</code></td><td><code>0.8</code></td><td>Minimum confidence score (0.0–1.0) to trigger detection</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h3 id="file-scan-config">FileScanConfig (v0.11)</h3>
  <p>Sub-configuration for prompt injection file scanning. Activates OCR on images, text extraction from PDF, and content analysis of Office documents.</p>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Field</th>
        <th>Type</th>
        <th>Default</th>
        <th>Description</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>enabled</code></td><td><code>bool</code></td><td><code>False</code></td><td>Enable/disable file scanning</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>scan_images</code></td><td><code>bool</code></td><td><code>True</code></td><td>Scan JPEG/PNG images via OCR</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>scan_pdf</code></td><td><code>bool</code></td><td><code>True</code></td><td>Scan PDF documents</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>scan_office</code></td><td><code>bool</code></td><td><code>True</code></td><td>Scan Office documents (DOCX/XLSX/PPTX)</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2 id="malware-config">MalwareConfig (v0.12)</h2>
  <p>Configures the <a href="/malware-scanning">Malware Scanning</a> module. All fields are optional.</p>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Field</th>
        <th>Type</th>
        <th>Default</th>
        <th>Description</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>enabled</code></td><td><code>bool</code></td><td><code>True</code></td><td>Enable/disable malware scanning</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>detectors</code></td><td><code>list[str]</code></td><td><code>["all"]</code></td><td>Subset of detectors: <code>"magic_bytes"</code>, <code>"mime_mismatch"</code>, <code>"zip_bomb"</code>, <code>"tar_bomb"</code>, <code>"office_macro"</code>, <code>"polyglot"</code>, <code>"double_extension"</code>, <code>"path_traversal"</code>, <code>"size_mismatch"</code></td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>archive_bomb_max_ratio</code></td><td><code>float</code></td><td><code>10.0</code></td><td>Max compression ratio before flagging as archive bomb</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>exclude_paths</code></td><td><code>list[str]</code></td><td><code>[]</code></td><td>Paths excluded from scanning</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2 id="graceful-shutdown">Graceful Shutdown</h2>
  <p>
    Araxys provides a <code>shield.shutdown()</code> method for <strong>graceful cleanup</strong> on application shutdown. This terminates all background tasks — session cleanup loops, webhook retry queues, and any other long-running background operations.
  </p>

  <div class="code-block">
    <div class="code-block-header">
      <span class="code-block-lang">python</span>
      <button class="code-block-copy">Copy</button>
    </div>
    <pre><code><span class="token-keyword">from</span> contextlib <span class="token-keyword">import</span> asynccontextmanager
<span class="token-keyword">from</span> fastapi <span class="token-keyword">import</span> FastAPI

<span class="token-decorator">@asynccontextmanager</span>
<span class="token-keyword">async def</span> <span class="token-function">lifespan</span>(<span class="token-param">app</span>: FastAPI):
    <span class="token-comment"># Startup</span>
    shield = <span class="token-function">AraxysShield</span>(app, config)
    <span class="token-keyword">yield</span>
    <span class="token-comment"># Shutdown — graceful cleanup</span>
    <span class="token-keyword">await</span> shield.<span class="token-function">shutdown</span>()

app = <span class="token-function">FastAPI</span>(<span class="token-param">lifespan</span>=lifespan)</code></pre>
  </div>

</DocsLayout>
